widgets_values:
参考我提供的提示词指南PDF和以下的提示词要求作为基本提示词要求：
【输入方式】:分镜= 主体（参考图描述）+ 场景（场景描述）+ 运动（运动描述）+ 美学控制 + 风格化 【延展目标】:基于上一张图的画面风格、人物外形、光影氛围、镜汇头语言，生成下一张分镜图，使得剧情延续，一共有多张分镜图，每张都要单独生成,保持人物外观一致色调光影与参考图统一背景元素延续，不突变构图具备电影感(景别/光影/空间层次)镜头类型(特写/中景/远景/俯拍/跟拍/环绕/侧移拉远)镜头运动节毒(慢推/快切/手持感)，除了逗号和句号，不要带其他符号。 人物发色、身形不变 服饰延续衔接，不跳变 动作表情是上一个镜头的自然推进 背景环境连续递进 高清画面 电影级光影 真实材质 无噪点无畸变 后续生成分镜时，严格遭循"人物外观(发色、身形、服饰)完全一致，色调光影与参考图统一、背景元素递进不突变的原则，每张分镜均采用电影级构图(明确景别、光影层次与空间关系)，搭配清晰的镜头类型与运动节奏，确保动作表情为上一镜头自然延续，同时保证画面高清、材质真实、无噪点畸变，可作为下一张分镜的生成基础。每一段镜头描述前都需要带有“Next Scene: ”。 輸出格式如下： Next Scene：...

nodes.title: Note(Copy the following to Gemini Or ChatGPT)
widgets_values:
Remember the following image generation prompt requirements as the base prompt style:
[Input method]: Storyboard = Subject (reference picture description) + Scene (scene description) + Movement (movement description) + Aesthetic control + Stylization [Extended goal]: Generate the next storyboard based on the style of the previous picture, the appearance of the characters, the atmosphere of light and shadow, and the language of the lens convergence to continue the plot. There are many continuous storyboards, each of which must be generated separately, keeping the appearance of the characters consistent, the color tone and light and shadow consistent with the reference picture, the background elements continue, and the composition does not change suddenly. It has a cinematic feel (scene/light and shadow/spatial level), lens type (close-up/medium shot/long shot/overhead shot/follow shot/surround/side shift and distance), lens movement mode (slow push/fast cut/handheld feel), and do not use other symbols except commas and periods. The character's hair color and body shape remain unchanged, clothing continues seamlessly without abrupt changes, movements and expressions are a natural progression from the previous shot, and the background environment progresses continuously. High-definition imagery, cinematic lighting, and realistic textures are employed, with no noise or distortion. When generating storyboards, we strictly adhere to the principles of maintaining a completely consistent character appearance (hair color, body shape, and clothing), consistent tonal and lighting tones with the reference image, and a progressive and seamless transition of background elements. Each storyboard utilizes cinematic composition (clearly defining the scene, light and shadow layers, and spatial relationships), along with clear shot types and movement rhythms to ensure a natural progression from the previous shot. High-definition imagery, realistic textures, and no noise or distortion are also ensured, serving as the foundation for the next storyboard. Each shot description must be preceded by "Next Scene: ." The output format is as follows: Next Scene: ..

Next Scene: Subject (A young woman with long dark hair, dressed in a black slip dress, lying on a white bed) + Scene (A hotel room with a warm, intimate atmosphere, soft lighting from a bedside lamp) + Movement (Her eyes are half-closed, a soft, sleepy smile on her lips, she slowly shifts her weight, her hand still gently resting on the pillow beneath her head, her body language is relaxed and seductive, a continuation of the previous pose) + Aesthetic control (High-definition imagery, cinematic warm lighting, realistic textures, no noise or distortion) + Stylization (Medium shot, slow push, natural progression of expression and body language, consistent character appearance, color tone, light and shadow, seamless background).
Next Scene: Subject (The young woman with long dark hair, dressed in a black slip dress, now with her head slightly lifted from the pillow, her gaze directly at the camera) + Scene (The same hotel room, warm and softly lit) + Movement (A playful, inviting smirk plays on her lips, her eyes are fully open and sparkling with a hint of mischief, her left hand slowly reaches up to playfully brush a strand of hair from her face, her body is still mostly prone but shows a subtle readiness to move) + Aesthetic control (High-definition imagery, cinematic warm lighting, realistic textures, no noise or distortion) + Stylization (Close-up, slow push, natural progression of expression and body language, consistent character appearance, color tone, light and shadow, seamless background).
Next Scene: Subject (The young woman, her dark hair slightly tousled, still in the black slip dress, now beginning to sit up slightly, her shoulders lifted) + Scene (The same hotel room, soft warm glow illuminating her face and the bed) + Movement (Her expression softens to a thoughtful, alluring look, her right arm is now supporting her as she props herself up, her eyes still holding that captivating gaze, a slight tilt of her head suggests she is listening or contemplating, her body is gracefully shifting upwards) + Aesthetic control (High-definition imagery, cinematic warm lighting, realistic textures, no noise or distortion) + Stylization (Medium shot, slow push, natural progression of expression and body language, consistent character appearance, color tone, light and shadow, seamless background).
Next Scene: Subject (The young woman, her dark hair falling gracefully around her shoulders, in the black slip dress, now fully sitting up at the edge of the bed) + Scene (The hotel room, with the soft light of the bedside lamp creating a gentle halo around her) + Movement (She crosses her legs elegantly, her hands resting casually in her lap, her gaze is now distant, thoughtful, almost wistful, as if she's looking out a window or into her own thoughts, her previous playful energy has subsided into a quiet introspection) + Aesthetic control (High-definition imagery, cinematic warm lighting, realistic textures, no noise or distortion) + Stylization (Medium long shot, slow push and side shift, natural progression of expression and body language, consistent character appearance, color tone, light and shadow, seamless background).
Next Scene: Subject (The young woman, her profile visible, with her long dark hair cascading over her shoulder, still in the black slip dress, as she stands beside the bed) + Scene (The hotel room, the bed is now slightly out of focus in the foreground, with her standing near a window, though the view outside is dark and indistinct) + Movement (She reaches out a hand to lightly touch the curtain, her head slightly bowed, a look of serene contemplation on her face, her body is slender and graceful, the movement is slow and deliberate, a quiet moment of reflection) + Aesthetic control (High-definition imagery, cinematic soft backlighting, realistic textures, no noise or distortion) + Stylization (Long shot, slow push, natural progression of expression and body language, consistent character appearance, color tone, light and shadow, seamless background).
Next Scene: Subject (The young woman, her back mostly to the camera, her silhouette softly defined by the light from the window, still in the black slip dress) + Scene (The hotel room, the window is now more prominent, showing the faint outline of a cityscape at night, lights twinkling) + Movement (She slowly turns her head to look back towards the bed, a faint, unreadable expression on her face, a sense of quiet longing or decision in her posture, her hand has dropped from the curtain, her body poised as if about to turn fully, a subtle shift of weight) + Aesthetic control (High-definition imagery, cinematic soft edge lighting, realistic textures, no noise or distortion) + Stylization (Long shot, slow push with a subtle surround, natural progression of expression and body language, consistent character appearance, color tone, light and shadow, seamless background).

The camera is low, looking up at the wizard from behind as he strides purposefully along a misty forest path. Ravens take flight around him. Suddenly, a gust of wind magic sweeps through the trees, making his robes and beard billow dramatically.

Video 2 Prompt
The wizard turns, facing the camera with an intense gaze. His hand, holding the staff, begins to glow. A flicker of lightning magic dances at the staff's tip, illuminating his face. The wind magic picks up, rustling leaves and creating an ominous atmosphere.

Video 3 Prompt
He raises his staff, and a powerful vortex of wind magic swirls around him, kicking up dust and leaves. Simultaneously, sparks of fire magic ignite from the ground where his feet stood, forming a protective, blazing circle around him.

Video 4 Prompt
The wizard unleashes a torrent of crackling lightning magic from his staff, striking a nearby ancient tree. The impact sends splinters flying and illuminates the dense forest. The wind magic intensifies, making the trees sway violently.

Video 5 Prompt
With a sweeping motion of his staff, the wizard commands the fire magic to surge forward in a blazing wave, chasing away the thick mist and revealing more of the dark forest beyond. The wind magic propels the flames with incredible force.

Video 6 Prompt
The wizard stands tall, a beacon of power amidst the receding magical chaos. Lingering tendrils of wind dissipate, and the last embers of fire fade. He lowers his staff, the air still buzzing with residual lightning energy, a triumphant look on his face as he resumes his journey deeper into the forest.
